However, it's for Wufeng's easy access.

32
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:20,980
At this point,

33
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:23,540
are you still trying to deny it?

34
00:03:30,430 --> 00:03:31,290
Wufeng's spies

35
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,340
must be killed.

36
00:03:33,290 --> 00:03:35,350
Execute her immediately right here.

37
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,500
Don't help me, Sword Wielder.

38
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:53,220
I lied to you.

39
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:56,710
I'm indeed Wufeng's spy.

40
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:04,170
Yun.

41
