They are all cosmetics.

121
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,040
Be careful with them.

122
00:14:13,210 --> 00:14:14,830
These are precious herbs.

123
00:14:14,930 --> 00:14:16,050
Plus those over there,

124
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,580
all the goods will be ready.

125
00:14:23,330 --> 00:14:24,830
Their footsteps are steady.

126
00:14:24,830 --> 00:14:26,890
The bottoms of their trousers are clean

127
00:14:26,890 --> 00:14:29,350
without any mud stains from goods delivery.

128
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:00,820
Chi, Mei, Wang, and Liang.

129
00:15:00,820 --> 00:15:02,580
The higher the level, the stronger they are.

130
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:04,380
Those who operate daily actions

131
00:15:04,430 --> 00:15:06,030
are of the levels Chi and Mei.

