00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:19,850
with independent jurisdiction.

141
00:15:19,850 --> 00:15:20,840
What about Liang?

142
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:22,570
Of course there are two of them.

143
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:24,500
But no one knows

144
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,100
their names and identities.

145
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:27,840
In fact,

146
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:31,520
no one even knows if Liang really exists.

147
00:15:32,370 --> 00:15:33,900
So even you haven't seen it?

148
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:38,780
I've only seen

149
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,180
three of the Wangs.

