00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:18,550
[True Heart True Medicine]

151
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:52,670
Lead the way.

152
00:16:53,830 --> 00:16:55,360
What are you talking about?

153
00:16:55,450 --> 00:16:56,380
I don't know you.

154
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,270
Stop pretending.

155
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:00,440
Take us to Wanhua Pavilion.

156
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:17,900
Young Master Hua.

