00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:20,599
Who wants to see me, you or Elder Hua?

158
00:17:21,119 --> 00:17:22,579
I've heard about Miss Yun.

159
00:17:25,619 --> 00:17:26,579
I also heard that

160
00:17:26,690 --> 00:17:29,620
you hacked off the old man's saber in just a few moves.

161
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,480
It seems that

162
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,920
my Heart Frost Saber is quite powerful.

163
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:38,050
The strongest saber

164
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:39,970
is never about the edge of killing,

165
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:41,350
but the blade of protection.

166
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:42,400
When you swung that saber,

167
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,460
the person you were trying to protect

168
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:45,120
must be very important to you.

169
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,200
Not just very.

170
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:53,760
She's the most important.

171
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,230
No matter what,

172
00:17:57,090 --> 00:17:58,330
I must protect her.

173
00:18:06,170 --> 00:18:07,770
When I was forging the saber,

174
00:18:07,970 --> 00:18:09,530
I already figured it out that

175
00:18:09,530 --> 00:18:11,060
the trial of the third realm

176
00:18:11,190 --> 00:18:13,650
