00:19:10,250 --> 00:19:13,690
[Three Forms of Mirror Flower]

200
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:16,890
Three Forms of Mirror Flower.

201
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:20,380
Learn it yourself.

202
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,090
Learn it myself?

203
00:19:24,450 --> 00:19:25,780
Shouldn't you teach me?

204
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:26,930
I don't know it.

205
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:29,300
Are you trying to slack off?

206
00:19:29,950 --> 00:19:31,400
Xue Chongzi and Young Master Yue

207
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,930
both taught me themselves.

208
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:34,110
I said I don't know it.

209
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:35,710
What I meant is I don't know how to teach you because I haven't learned it myself.

210
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,100
It's not that I don't want to teach you.

211
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,150
My hands are tied.

212
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:41,510
Really?

213
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:46,720
Your eyes are full of contempt and sarcasm.

214
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,250
I'm so sad.

215
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:50,820
You've been in the back hill for so many years,

216
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:54,410
