217
00:19:54,410 --> 00:19:55,140
You know that

218
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:57,940
the saber techniques of Snow, Moon, and Flower

219
00:19:57,940 --> 00:19:59,640
become harder level by level, right?

220
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,270
I know.

221
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:02,210
So the Three Forms of Mirror Flower

222
00:20:02,210 --> 00:20:04,680
are the most difficult three forms among all the saber techniques.

223
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,690
If I could master

224
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:07,140
such hard saber techniques,

225
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:08,170
I wouldn't be scolded

226
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:09,500
by that old man all day.

227
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:15,070
So, did my brother and Gong Shangjue

228
00:20:15,170 --> 00:20:17,900
learn the Three Forms of Mirror Flower when they left?

229
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:19,230
No, neither of them did.

230
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,610
Gong Huanyu and Gong Shangjue only learned the first form.

231
00:20:22,610 --> 00:20:24,560
The former Sword Wielder learned the essence of the second form,

232
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:25,760
but he stopped there.

233
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:39,830
Stop pretending.

234
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:41,740
As if you can understand.

235
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:44,730
Go back and take your time to learn it.

236
00:20:47,360 --> 00:20:47,960
Okay.

237
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:50,710
It's not over yet.

238
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:51,410
Keep the scripture well

239
00:20:51,410 --> 00:20:52,340
and come with me.

240
00:21:13,410 --> 00:21:14,610
Since you have passed

241
00:21:14,730 --> 00:21:16,100
the Trial of the Three Realms,

242
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:17,430
it's time to let you know

243
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:20,030
the biggest secret of the Gong family.

244
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:23,350
A century ago,

245
00:21:23,890 --> 00:21:25,260
the first Sword Wielder of the Gong family

246
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:28,190
came here with the three families, Xue, Yue, and Hua.

247
00:21:28,260 --> 00:21:29,590
He made a blood oath that

248
00:21:30,050 --> 00:21:31,240
his descendants would

249
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:33,930
guard the back hill generation after generation.

250
00:21:33,930 --> 00:21:35,060
However, actually,

251
00:21:35,170 --> 00:21:37,300
