252
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:40,150
somewhere deep in the back hill of the Gong residence.

253
00:21:40,150 --> 00:21:41,410
Guarding the back hill

254
00:21:41,770 --> 00:21:43,900
is to protect the people and the world.

255
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:48,120
After the three residences of Xue, Yue, and Hua were built,

256
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,040
the first Sword Wielder

257
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,510
built another four residences,

258
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,390
namely Shang, Jue,

259
00:21:51,390 --> 00:21:52,050
Zhi, and Yu,

260
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:53,320
in the front hill.

261
00:21:54,230 --> 00:21:55,110
People in the martial world

262
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:57,610
only know how powerful the front hill of the Gong family is.

263
00:21:57,610 --> 00:21:58,890
But they don't know that the core of it

264
00:21:58,890 --> 00:22:01,140
is the support of the Xue, Yue, and Hua families.

265
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:04,310
If the front hill is the flesh and blood of the Gong family,

266
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:05,310
then the back hill

267
00:22:05,510 --> 00:22:07,310
is where the heart arteries are.

268
00:22:10,220 --> 00:22:12,110
The three families, Xue, Yue, and Hua

269
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:14,920
made use of the meteorite falling from the sky in the valley

270
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:17,890
and developed the extraordinarily powerful Infinite Heat.

271
00:22:17,890 --> 00:22:19,340
They did that in case

272
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:21,790
one day the infidels get out of control,

273
00:22:22,170 --> 00:22:23,690
they'll perish with them.

274
00:22:26,230 --> 00:22:28,520
But the Infinite Heat is too powerful.

275
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:30,250
Once it falls into

276
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,940
some vicious people's hands,

277
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:34,590
the consequences would be unimaginable.

278
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:35,160
So

279
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:37,280
the families agreed

280
00:22:37,870 --> 00:22:40,330
