282
00:22:42,380 --> 00:22:43,620
as well.

283
00:22:44,510 --> 00:22:46,630
If it's not for the survival of the Gong family,

284
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:48,270
it should never be activated.

285
00:22:48,270 --> 00:22:51,130
So this is the Infinite Heat you were talking about.

286
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:54,340
No wonder Infinite Heat has never been used to counter Wufeng

287
00:22:54,340 --> 00:22:56,040
despite how powerful it is.

288
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:57,340
Exactly.

289
00:22:58,160 --> 00:23:00,070
The power of Infinite Heat

290
00:23:00,520 --> 00:23:03,330
should be used to deal with the infidels in the back hill,

291
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:05,080
not the people in the mortal world.

292
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:06,480
So why are there infidels

293
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:08,120
in the back hill?

294
00:23:08,710 --> 00:23:09,910
Who exactly are they?

295
00:23:12,430 --> 00:23:13,460
No one knows.

296
00:23:14,210 --> 00:23:14,820
Anyway,

297
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:17,220
the rule passed down by the ancestors

298
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:19,260
is to guard the back hill.

299
00:23:20,080 --> 00:23:23,020
This is also a secret precautiously protected by the back hill.

300
00:23:23,020 --> 00:23:25,480
You've become the Sword Wielder of the Gong family.

301
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:26,150
Remember.

302
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:29,430
You can't make judgments based on your own preferences.

303
00:23:29,740 --> 00:23:31,200
Activating Infinite Heat

304
00:23:31,380 --> 00:23:33,880
is a significant matter concerning all the people's safety.

305
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:34,720
You must

306
00:23:34,970 --> 00:23:36,000
abide by

307
00:23:36,210 --> 00:23:37,670
the will of the ancestors.

308
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:39,090
I understand.

309
00:23:41,170 --> 00:23:42,620
Why didn't Wuji kill you?

310
00:23:43,250 --> 00:23:44,760
Why did she go through so much trouble

311
00:23:44,760 --> 00:23:45,690
to imprison you?

312
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:49,450
What she wants

313
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:52,160
is that thing in Hua Residence, of course.

314
00:23:57,010 --> 00:23:58,610
Could the reason why Lady...

315
00:24:03,320 --> 00:24:04,720
Could the reason why Wuji

316
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:06,610
imprisoned my brother

317
00:24:06,910 --> 00:24:07,980
be to press him

318
00:24:08,340 --> 00:24:09,640
for the Infinite Heat?

319
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,240
That's right.

320
00:24:15,900 --> 00:24:16,870
How did Lady Wuji

321
00:24:17,370 --> 00:24:19,370
get to know the Infinite Heat, then?

322
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,580
I'm afraid she was full of tricks,

323
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:23,110
so she managed to get this secret

324
00:24:23,110 --> 00:24:24,910
out of the former Sword Wielder.

325
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:31,300
Do you remember

326
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:34,800
the hairpin that got the former Sword Wielder killed?

327
00:24:35,150 --> 00:24:36,150
What Huanyu found

328
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,920
in that hairpin

329
00:24:38,190 --> 00:24:41,110
was information about the Infinite Heat.

330
00:24:41,570 --> 00:24:44,910
That's why he hurriedly brought Zheng Nanyi and the hairpin

331
00:24:45,020 --> 00:24:46,550
to the former Sword Wielder

332
00:24:47,310 --> 00:24:48,240
without knowing

333
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:49,560
that all of this

334
00:24:49,850 --> 00:24:52,380
was a plot to murder the former Sword Wielder.

335
00:24:52,810 --> 00:24:54,210
Now that I think about it,

336
00:24:54,810 --> 00:24:55,880
it must be Wuji

337
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,820
who told Zheng Nanyi about it.

338
00:24:58,890 --> 00:24:59,830
I see.

339
00:25:02,330 --> 00:25:04,310
So did Gong Shangjue leave that night

340
00:25:04,310 --> 00:25:05,770
also to investigate this?

341
00:25:06,340 --> 00:25:07,000
Shangjue.

342
00:25:07,670 --> 00:25:08,490
Please

343
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:10,000
go to the Zheng family.

344
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:11,660
Yes.

345
00:25:14,460 --> 00:25:17,140
All the misunderstandings and conflicts between you and Shangjue

346
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:18,200
started from this.

347
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:20,460
Now that you've got to know everything,

348
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:22,390
don't get into any more conflicts.

349
00:25:22,630 --> 00:25:24,250
Although what Shangjue has done

350
00:25:24,250 --> 00:25:25,420
is harsh,

351
00:25:25,650 --> 00:25:27,650
what he did is all for the good of the Gong family.

352
00:25:27,650 --> 00:25:29,780
His suspicions of Wuji and Yun Weishan

353
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,340
have also been confirmed.

354
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:33,740
You are of the same blood.

355
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,800
You are biological brothers.

356
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,600
In the future,

357
00:25:36,730 --> 00:25:38,300
you should work together.

358
00:25:39,330 --> 00:25:40,230
One more thing.

359
00:25:41,070 --> 00:25:42,630
Since Yun Weishan has left,

360
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:45,000
at your accession ceremony,

361
00:25:45,510 --> 00:25:47,170
you need to select a new bride.

362
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:48,780
The Sword Wielder

363
00:25:49,210 --> 00:25:51,140
can't be unmarried and childless.

364
00:25:52,190 --> 00:25:52,900
Elder Xue.

365
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:53,720
This...

366
00:25:53,810 --> 00:25:55,510
Let's make it five days from now.

367
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:56,570
Five days from now,

368
00:25:56,730 --> 00:25:57,970
the five stars will come together,

369
00:25:57,970 --> 00:25:59,230
and the sun and the moon will collide.

370
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:00,630
It's an auspicious omen.

371
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:12,550
Elders.

372
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:13,220
Sword Wielder.

373
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:15,030
There was an explosion

374
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:18,200
in Eldest Young Miss Gong Zishang's research lab.

375
00:26:25,570 --> 00:26:28,870
[Shang]

376
00:26:48,410 --> 00:26:50,140
You should wrap your wound too.

377
00:26:57,450 --> 00:26:59,040
When I held her just now,

378
00:27:01,860 --> 00:27:03,540
I almost couldn't feel her.

379
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:10,830
They say

380
00:27:12,890 --> 00:27:14,150
simple-minded people

381
00:27:15,050 --> 00:27:16,310
are blessed and lucky.

382
00:27:19,670 --> 00:27:20,600
I'm sure Zishang

383
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:22,360
will be fine.

384
00:27:39,210 --> 00:27:40,030
How is she?

385
00:27:42,580 --> 00:27:44,110
Eldest Young Miss is smart.

386
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:47,120
She wetted her body with water during the explosion

387
00:27:47,130 --> 00:27:48,930
and covered her head with cloth.

388
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:51,210
So her skin wasn't severely burnt.

389
00:27:52,950 --> 00:27:54,360
But continuous explosions

390
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:55,640
caused strong impact.

391
00:27:56,590 --> 00:27:57,320
Her head,

392
00:27:57,580 --> 00:27:58,440
heart and lungs

393
00:27:58,790 --> 00:28:01,170
suffered concussions to different degrees,

394
00:28:01,170 --> 00:28:02,300
which led to coma.

395
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:07,960
We have applied a skin-restoring dressing on her wounds,

396
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:10,640
and silver needles to protect her heart and lungs.

397
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:11,380
But

398
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:15,960
it's up to her fate

399
00:28:16,970 --> 00:28:18,300
if she's going to wake up

400
00:28:18,650 --> 00:28:19,700
and when.

401
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:26,070
Is there no other way?

402
00:28:29,370 --> 00:28:32,790
I'll give her acupuncture every day to recuperate her meridians.

403
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:33,400
As for you,

404
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:35,650
you can talk to her more.

405
00:28:42,620 --> 00:28:43,680
Eldest Young Miss.

406
00:28:46,970 --> 00:28:48,570
Can you hear me?

407
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:04,410
Let's go.

408
00:29:20,730 --> 00:29:22,260
I've been hiding something

409
00:29:25,710 --> 00:29:26,600
in my heart

410
00:29:30,230 --> 00:29:31,830
that I didn't tell you.

411
00:29:33,970 --> 00:29:35,060
You kept asking me

412
00:29:36,340 --> 00:29:37,350
every day.

413
00:29:41,870 --> 00:29:43,470
It's not that I don't want to.

414
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:47,800
It's because I dare not.

415
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:54,940
Since the day I became Green Jade Guardian,

416
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:58,680
I've only existed to protect Gong Ziyu.

417
00:30:02,250 --> 00:30:03,070
Life and death

418
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,800
is not even up to me.

419
00:30:12,550 --> 00:30:15,280
I'm not qualified to accept your feelings for me.

420
00:30:22,990 --> 00:30:24,900
But now I regret it.

421
00:30:27,150 --> 00:30:27,900
I regret it.

422
00:30:29,690 --> 00:30:32,210
How nice would it be

423
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:37,080
to have let you know my feelings?

424
00:30:49,190 --> 00:30:51,250
The fire on the ruins has been put out.

425
00:30:51,330 --> 00:30:52,530
It's a complete mess.

426
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:57,380
Those from the Council of Elders are still investigating in the ruins.

427
00:30:58,370 --> 00:30:59,970
Gong Shangjue was there too.

428
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:05,550
The fire and explosion took place out of the blue.

429
00:31:05,550 --> 00:31:06,950
It's indeed suspicious.

430
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:08,220
Have you found

431
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:09,280
anything unusual?

432
00:31:10,110 --> 00:31:11,370
I asked a few servants.

433
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:12,610
They all said

434
00:31:13,410 --> 00:31:14,610
they saw Gong Yuanzhi

435
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:15,960
having an argument

436
00:31:16,180 --> 00:31:16,860
with Gong Zishang

437
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:18,120
before the explosion.

438
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:20,310
Gong Yuanzhi...

439
00:31:21,560 --> 00:31:22,760
It was about Miss Yun.

440
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,180
Stop there!

441
00:31:24,340 --> 00:31:25,620
Can't you hear me?

442
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,540
Shut up!

443
00:31:26,690 --> 00:31:28,090
This is my house. Get out.

444
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:29,760
You cover up for Wufeng

445
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,370
like Gong Ziyu does.

446
00:31:31,670 --> 00:31:33,580
He doesn't deserve to be the Sword Wielder of the Gong family.

447
00:31:33,580 --> 00:31:34,650
And you don't deserve to be

448
00:31:34,650 --> 00:31:35,740
the head of Shang Lineage either.

449
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:36,750
Whether a person is good or bad

450
00:31:36,750 --> 00:31:38,100
shouldn't be judged by their identity.

451
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:39,230
You need to feel it by heart.

452
00:31:39,230 --> 00:31:40,560
Do you understand that?

453
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:42,290
Miss Yun has never hurt anyone.

454
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:44,840
You don't have a heart.

455
00:31:44,840 --> 00:31:46,710
Of course you wouldn't understand.

456
00:31:46,710 --> 00:31:47,490
Ridiculous.

457
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:50,390
You're both blinded by that spy from Wufeng.

458
00:31:50,390 --> 00:31:51,790
If she were a good person,

459
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,770
why would she secretly draw the map

460
00:31:53,770 --> 00:31:55,700
and lead Wufeng to break into the Gong Residence?

461
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:58,580
I left the Gong Residence and went down the hill with Miss Yun once.

462
00:31:58,580 --> 00:31:59,970
If she had that intention,

463
00:31:59,970 --> 00:32:02,050
the map would have been in Wufeng's hands long ago.

464
00:32:02,050 --> 00:32:03,650
How could she let you find it?

465
00:32:03,770 --> 00:32:05,560
She has long defected to us.

466
00:32:05,810 --> 00:32:07,940
She's always been on Gong Ziyu's side.

467
00:32:08,270 --> 00:32:09,970
You drove her away.

468
00:32:10,140 --> 00:32:10,960
Idiot.

469
00:32:12,850 --> 00:32:15,050
No wonder your father hates you so much.

470
00:32:33,330 --> 00:32:34,170
This fragment

471
00:32:34,470 --> 00:32:36,290
was found in the ruins of the warehouse.

472
00:32:36,290 --> 00:32:37,740
This is from the golden silk gloves

473
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:39,670
for Gong Yuanzhi's exclusive use.

474
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:41,860
Are you concluding that it was Brother Yuanzhi who did it

475
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:43,650
just for a fragment of a glove?

476
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:47,410
It could have accidentally dropped there when they had that argument.

477
00:32:47,410 --> 00:32:48,230
Or maybe

478
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:49,300
he was framed.

479
00:32:49,610 --> 00:32:51,940
Aren't you being too rash, Sword Wielder?

480
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:56,650
Young Master Shangjue, you've always been fair and strict.

481
00:32:56,650 --> 00:32:58,460
You've never had selfish intentions.

482
00:32:58,460 --> 00:33:00,060
Why are you trying to cover up

483
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:02,430
when it comes to your brother?

484
00:33:02,430 --> 00:33:04,090
Verbal aguments are useless.

485
00:33:04,890 --> 00:33:06,320
When Gong Zishang wakes up,

486
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,620
the truth will be revealed.

487
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:08,100
Fine.

488
00:33:09,090 --> 00:33:10,440
When Zishang wakes up,

489
00:33:11,300 --> 00:33:14,360
she will definitely accuse Gong Yuanzhi of what he did.

490
00:33:15,250 --> 00:33:18,320
What if Zishang couldn't wake up?

491
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:37,120
[Feng]

492
00:33:40,420 --> 00:33:41,760
When will the battle start?

493
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:42,540
In five days.

494
00:33:44,770 --> 00:33:46,570
Why do we have to wait for five days?

495
00:33:46,570 --> 00:33:48,840
The information was sent by Shangguan Qian,

496
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:51,240
a Wufeng spy of level Mei in the Gong family.

497
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:54,910
Hanya Si.

498
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:57,240
We met your subordinate on the way.

499
00:33:58,530 --> 00:34:00,100
Do you want to talk to her?

500
00:34:04,010 --> 00:34:05,410
Why did you run into them?

501
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:06,780
You should ask

502
00:34:07,020 --> 00:34:08,820
why she left the Gong Residence.

503
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:17,250
I had lost my gloves before the explosion.

504
00:34:17,250 --> 00:34:19,650
I sent someone to look for it for a long time.

505
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:22,280
I didn't expect them to frame me with it.

506
00:34:22,370 --> 00:34:23,969
Gong Ziyu is so scheming.

507
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:25,780
So vicious.

508
00:34:30,590 --> 00:34:33,050
It must be because you two young masters forced Yun Weishan to leave

509
00:34:33,050 --> 00:34:34,580
that he wouldn't let you go.

510
00:34:36,429 --> 00:34:38,280
They set you up and wronged you like that, Brother Yuanzhi.

511
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:40,540
Young Master won't sit by and do nothing.

512
00:34:41,219 --> 00:34:43,080
Brother Yuanzhi, don't be angry.

513
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,610
They have no solid evidence.

514
00:34:46,469 --> 00:34:48,340
They can't do anything to Yuanzhi.

515
00:34:48,340 --> 00:34:50,739
The date of Gong Ziyu's accession ceremony

516
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,040
has been set.

517
00:34:54,310 --> 00:34:55,510
It's already settled

518
00:34:57,210 --> 00:34:59,010
that he'll be the Sword Wielder.

519
00:34:59,620 --> 00:35:01,020
At this critical moment,

520
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:02,420
it's no good for us

521
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:04,980
to confront him head-on.

522
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,440
Accession ceremony?

523
00:35:09,310 --> 00:35:09,820
Yes.

524
00:35:12,670 --> 00:35:13,740
In five days.

525
00:35:16,450 --> 00:35:17,340
In five days?

526
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:19,370
Why did they choose this...

527
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:25,750
They must have chosen that date

528
00:35:25,780 --> 00:35:26,640
on purpose.

529
00:35:27,210 --> 00:35:27,740
Brother.

530
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:29,190
This is too much.

531
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:32,170
Tell Gong Ziyu that

532
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:33,680
there will be a celestial phenomenon of five stars coming together

533
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,510
ten days from now.

534
00:35:36,290 --> 00:35:38,490
Let him set the date of the accession ceremony

535
00:35:38,490 --> 00:35:39,400
to that day.

536
00:35:41,580 --> 00:35:42,210
Why?

537
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:45,450
Taking advantage of their internal conflict,

538
00:35:45,450 --> 00:35:46,540
gather the elite,

539
00:35:47,700 --> 00:35:49,940
break into the Gong Residence

540
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:52,710
when Gong Shangjue's the weakest,

541
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:53,800
and catch them all.

542
00:35:54,650 --> 00:35:56,310
Don't worry about the reason.

543
00:35:56,370 --> 00:35:57,470
Just do it.

544
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,700
It'll be no use telling Gong Ziyu.

545
00:36:07,070 --> 00:36:08,270
It's too deliberate,

546
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,290
so it'll be suspicious.

547
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:13,890
Let the Elder tell him.

548
00:36:14,590 --> 00:36:15,650
It's more natural,

549
00:36:15,950 --> 00:36:17,550
and no one will be against it.

550
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:19,950
I'll find a way

551
00:36:20,300 --> 00:36:21,560
to persuade Elder Yue.

552
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:22,660
One more thing.

553
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:25,150
Since Yun Weishan has left,

554
00:36:25,770 --> 00:36:27,430
you must select a new bride

555
00:36:28,030 --> 00:36:29,630
at your accession ceremony.

556
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:31,520
Let's make it five days from now.

557
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:33,440
Five days from now,

558
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:34,740
five stars will come together,

559
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:36,100
and the sun and the moon will collide.

560
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:37,450
It's an auspicious omen.

561
00:36:37,450 --> 00:36:39,850
After Gong Ziyu becomes the Sword Wielder,

562
00:36:39,910 --> 00:36:41,840
we'll have to answer to him, right?

563
00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:44,950
