729
00:47:00,080 --> 00:47:01,610
Hanya is even more pitiful.

730
00:47:04,180 --> 00:47:05,710
They only belong to winter.

731
00:47:07,350 --> 00:47:09,010
They don't deserve the light.

732
00:47:11,440 --> 00:47:12,840
They only deserve to live

733
00:47:13,860 --> 00:47:15,260
